metadata.name: Serene Morning
metadata.description:
In Blossom Park, a serene morning break,  
The world awakens, and nature awakens,  
The dew on petals, like crystal flakes,  
A morning so peaceful, it takes my soul.

The cherry trees in bloom, a lake of pink,  
A symphony of colors, a joyful link,  
The fragrance is sweet, enough to drink,  
A moment so blissful, I stop and think.

The birds chirp merrily, a song so sweet,  
Their melodies, a morning treat,  
A tranquil moment, hard to beat,  
In Blossom Park, where the world meets.

The sun rises high, and warms the air,  
The breeze whispers softly, without care,  
The flowers sway, as if to share,  
Their beauty, with all who dare.

In Blossom Park, a serene morning unfolds,  
A moment in time, forever told,  
A place where peace and nature hold,  
A precious gem, of pure gold.

明华 MingHua - 2023
